'''Hurlothrombic gas''' was a substance that would produce a state of fear in organic beings that were exposed to the compound. Its effects were similar to the [[hurlothrombic generator]] and it was known that the [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] would often flood his audience chambers with the gas to leave his guests in a constant state of fear.

